  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100219/love-header.jpg" alt="loveofhero" data-udi="umb://media/8aa858c2ca2646f6aa73c0f0037f33b3" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p>However you enjoy the mountains, do it <strong>for the love of ski</strong>. We’re calling out to the thrill seekers, the pit stoppers, the mountain lovers, the après skiers, and… the sit back and relaxers. Get your ski fix this winter, check out our huge range of resorts, hotels and offers. <strong>For the love of... winning? Enter our competition!</strong></p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100135/icy-blue-down-left-arrow.png" alt="6arrow" data-udi="umb://media/e1c52266d5f14e4fa91f368a318ab82d" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic">
<h2 id="entercompetition" style="text-align: left;">For the love of...<em>winning</em></h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Enter our competition for a chance to win a <em>7 night ski holiday, </em>all you have to do is let us know what you LOVE to do on a ski holiday, are you a thrill seeker, a pit stopper, a mountain lover, an après skier or a sit back and relaxer?</p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;">To <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></strong></li>
<li style="text-align: left;">For 2 people</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">In the 3* <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/4b760957e37d406ebac427082e171ece" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4b760957e37d406ebac427082e171ece}" title="Hotel Terrace">Hotel Terrace</a></strong> in <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/313f2f0348a742b4989db3458bb4a71a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/313f2f0348a742b4989db3458bb4a71a}" title="Engelberg">Engelberg</a></strong></li>
<li style="text-align: left;">On a half board basis</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Flights and transfers included</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">7 day Lift passes for 2</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: left;">All of this, for next ski season - 2025. </p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/313f2f0348a742b4989db3458bb4a71a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/313f2f0348a742b4989db3458bb4a71a}" class="c-btn">Engelberg Resort</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Terms and conditions for entering the competition can be found <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e5a28f150750481d8ca3006d7d3baa4b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5a28f150750481d8ca3006d7d3baa4b}" title="For the love of ski competition">here</a></strong>. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><strong><br /><br />This competition has now closed as of the 12th April 2024</strong><br /><br /><img src="/media/13101947/quality-time-for-the-family-ski_juwel_alpbachtal_wildschoenau.jpg" alt="ForTheLoveComp" data-udi="umb://media/cb937ac5225a40dabe89a63e6a69c9f5" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;">The winner of the competition will be / has been contacted via email.</p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100136/icy-blue-down-right-arrow.png" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/958f28de8f8d4d089bb2f43279cfc8c2" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic"><img src="/media/13099805/mountain-lovers-520x520.jpg" alt="mountainlovers" data-udi="umb://media/ea0acc19cadc421c9279d5d8df308104" /></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic">
<h2 style="text-align: left;">For the love of...<em>mountains</em></h2>
<p>Every holiday with Inghams brings you closer to the great outdoors to enjoy those once in a lifetime moments!</p>
<p>For those who love to explore new <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" title="Ski Resorts">destinations</a></strong> and ski new slopes each year, you’ve come to the right place, with destinations across Europe and <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">Canada</a></strong>.</p>
<p>Sometimes it is about the journey as well as the destination. New for 2023/24, Inghams are offering ski packages including <a data-udi="umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5}" title="Ski holidays by train" data-anchor="#"><strong>train travel</strong>.</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100135/icy-blue-down-left-arrow.png" alt="2arrow" data-udi="umb://media/e1c52266d5f14e4fa91f368a318ab82d" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic">
<h2 style="text-align: left;">For the love of...<em>first lifts</em></h2>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>There is nothing quite like that first morning lift - when the sky is blue, the slopes are empty and you can feel the freedom ahead. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>If blue-bird mornings are for you, and the first lift isn’t early enough, book a ski holiday with </span><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b}" title="Ski In Ski Out Holidays">ski-in ski-out</a></strong><span> access as the priority.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>If you are searching for the perfect piste, know where to go with our <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/b28019985984419899535b05fb4b9b57" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b28019985984419899535b05fb4b9b57}" title="Insider’s Guide: Top 10 snow-sure ski resorts in Europe">Top Snow Sure Resorts</a></strong> guide.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>For this season, the stunning <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89}" title="Livigno">Livigno Resort</a></strong> in Italy is offering a <em>free 6 day ski pass</em> for guests arriving on the 16th December:</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89}" title="Livigno" class="c-btn">Livigno free pass</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic"><img src="/media/13099564/love-of-first-lifts-520x520.jpg" alt="offirstlifts" data-udi="umb://media/63296d7bc3614fa585d960f0def65027" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100136/icy-blue-down-right-arrow.png" alt="3arrow" data-udi="umb://media/958f28de8f8d4d089bb2f43279cfc8c2" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic"><img src="/media/13099645/love-of-thrill-520x520.jpg" alt="of thrill" data-udi="umb://media/97de3d4ccd094d81abd0773c51c92704" /></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic">
<h2 style="text-align: left;">For the love of...<em>the thrill</em></h2>
<p>Skiing holidays are all about the thrill of downhill. For those thrill-seekers out there with all the mountain knowledge, we offer some of the best ski resorts for <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb}" title="Skiing for Advanced">advanced skiers</a></strong> looking to test their skills, see more of the mountains and have a sense of adventure.</p>
<p>If you really want to push your limits, read our <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/af7148e637c544699734b64f3e5c3be8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af7148e637c544699734b64f3e5c3be8}" title="Insider's Guide: Top 5 scary ski runs">Top Scary Runs</a></strong> guide across resorts to find your next destination.</p>
<p>Already dreaming of creating the first tracks of the day down the most challenging runs? Pre-order your ski-pass and ski hire equipment:</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/88813b4c856349a88af3cf6c8780d098" href="/{localLink:umb://document/88813b4c856349a88af3cf6c8780d098}" title="Ski Hire" class="c-btn">View ski hire</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100135/icy-blue-down-left-arrow.png" alt="4arrow" data-udi="umb://media/e1c52266d5f14e4fa91f368a318ab82d" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic">
<h2 style="text-align: left;">For the love of...<em>après</em> </h2>
<p>Fun off the slopes is just as important as on the slopes, and that’s what <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079}" title="Apres Ski Holidays">Après ski holidays</a></strong> are all about.</p>
<p>Get together with friends, family and locals in some of the coolest après bars, clubs, cafés and restaurants that resorts have to offer. Try a local tipple or 2, get out on the dance floor or enjoy some live sax music.</p>
<p>Check out our top choices on where to enjoy some après fun this season - <a data-udi="umb://document/af40d2b697b74b82b2baaa9df968232c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af40d2b697b74b82b2baaa9df968232c}" title="Insider's Guide: Top Apres Ski Bars">Best Après Ski Resorts Guide</a></p>
<p>Stay in some of the best locations across Europe, including popular après ski resorts, with our <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0}" title="Inghams Choice Accommodation">Inghams Choice</a></strong> properties - hand-picked accommodation that we know you will enjoy. </p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/49b9c2d67d104ca3879a39351d601ab0}" title="Inghams Choice Accommodation" class="c-btn">Inghams choice</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic"><img src="/media/13099646/love-of-apres-520x520.jpg" alt="ofapres" data-udi="umb://media/4e1d786e61334d4d9ad9b550e051d8cd" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100136/icy-blue-down-right-arrow.png" alt="5arrow" data-udi="umb://media/958f28de8f8d4d089bb2f43279cfc8c2" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic"><img src="/media/13099647/love-of-relax-520x520.jpg" alt="ofrelax" data-udi="umb://media/14c4738b42d34ec0952f1f69beeb0dd1" /></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic">
<h2 style="text-align: left;">For the love of...<em>relaxing</em></h2>
<p>Sit back, relax and enjoy the moment. Take a peaceful moment for yourself whilst you ease away a days skiing in a bubbling hot-tub and warm sauna.</p>
<p>We have some amazing <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46}" title="Ski &amp; Spa Holidays">luxury and spa accommodations</a></strong> across our resorts, so no matter where you like to ski, you can come back to comfort.</p>
<p>Hoping to elevate your time away, then read our guide on <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/5c42a28aa7a646c5a359c5922406806f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c42a28aa7a646c5a359c5922406806f}" title="Insider's Guide: Most romantic ski destinations">Most Romantic Resorts</a></strong> to plan some extra special touches to your skiing holiday.</p>
<p>Make your love of ski a reality this coming winter - see all our <em>2024/25 deals, with extra special offers over Christmas and New Year: </em></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb}" title="December" class="c-btn">Christmas &amp; New Year</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-page-content">
<p><img src="/media/13100135/icy-blue-down-left-arrow.png" alt="6arrow" data-udi="umb://media/e1c52266d5f14e4fa91f368a318ab82d" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
